<!-- ABOUT TEASER -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="about-teaser">
    <div class="about-text">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">About Me</div>
      <h2>Thoughtful learning, <em>by design.</em></h2>
      <p class="section-intro" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">At Lumen Learning, I design and lead the development of high-enrollment digital courses across the social sciences. My courses have reached over 400,000 learners, and my Introductory Psychology course is consistently the highest-enrolled course on the platform.</p>
      <p class="section-intro" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">I have the mentality of a teacher and a coach. I loved my years in the high school classroom and still feel passionately about supporting both the learner and the instructor. Over the years I've built everything from full courses to instructor guides, interactives, games, and assessments. That same instinct carries into how I work with teams — I get genuine satisfaction from mentoring designers, helping people push their thinking, and watching someone take an idea further than expected.</p>
      <p class="section-intro">I've taught with the products I build. As an adjunct professor at Davidson College, I piloted my own course design live in a face-to-face classroom and loved both interacting with the students and iterating on the courseware. I never shy away from a challenge and revel in the opportunity to combine my love of teaching with the latest research in learning design and emerging technologies.</p>
      <blockquote class="about-quote">"Education is not preparation for life; education is life itself." — John Dewey</blockquote>
      <a href="{{ '/about/' | url }}" class="btn-primary">Read My Full Story &rarr;</a>
    </div>
